<h1 id=3D"id-02SD:BeneficiaryManagementEntitlement-Solution"><span>Solution=
</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-02SD:BeneficiaryManagementEntitlement-SolutionOverview"><span>=
Solution Overview</span></h2>
<p><span>The Solution covers at the following scenarios:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Beneficiary to Organisation attribution in Neptune</span>
<ul>
<li><span>Creation of new Beneficiary resource in Entitlements.</span></li>
<li><span>Creation of 'All Beneficiaries' scope under Organisation in the N=
eptune database</span></li>
<li><span>Manual load of sample beneficiaries from new Beneficiary DB to Or=
ganisation for May ERM.</span>
<ul>
<li><span>Will support Neptune data load during testing phases.</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span>Creation of new Beneficiary actions that can be assigned to subje=
cts:</span>
<ul>
<li><span>ViewBeneficiary (this would probably be inherited as part of paym=
ents personas)</span></li>
<li><span>CreateBeneficiary</span></li>
<li><span>ModifyBeneficiary</span></li>
<li><span>ArchiveBeneficiary</span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span>New beneficiary policy that secures beneficiary creation.</span>
<ul>
<li><span>The policy must:</span>
<ul>
<li><span>Return a list of beneficiaries available to that organisation via=
 the query functionality.</span>
<ul>
<li><span>Uplift of query library, might need organisation to be able to fi=
lter for multi org customers.</span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span>Must only allow users with the appropriate actions to interact wi=
th beneficiaries creation experience.</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span>Uplift of any client or server side libraries to include new acti=
ons.</span>
<ul>
<li><span><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/143=
60+-+Architecture+For+Entitlements+Information#id-14360ArchitectureForEntit=
lementsInformation-MFECliententitlements" rel=3D"nofollow">MFE Client Libra=
ry</a></span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-02SD:BeneficiaryManagementEntitlement-SequenceDiagram"><span>S=
equence Diagram</span></h2>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-02SD:BeneficiaryManagementEntitlement-IntegrationDiagram">Inte=
gration Diagram</h2>
<p></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Entitlement vouch calls</strong></p>
<p>The following beneficiaries endpoints should be intercepted by PEP:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"1"><a href=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/exp-galaxy-beneficiary-v1#expgalaxy=
beneficiaryv1-GET/beneficiaries/summary" class=3D"toc-link" rel=3D"nofollow=
">GET /beneficiaries/summary</a></span></li>
<li><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"2"><a href=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/exp-galaxy-beneficiary-v1#expgalaxy=
beneficiaryv1-POST/beneficiaries/detail/id" class=3D"toc-link" rel=3D"nofol=
low">POST /beneficiaries/detail/id</a></span></li>
<li><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"3"><a href=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/exp-galaxy-beneficiary-v1#expgalaxy=
beneficiaryv1-POST/beneficiaries" class=3D"toc-link" rel=3D"nofollow">POST =
/beneficiaries</a></span></li>
<li><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"4"><a href=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/exp-galaxy-beneficiary-v1#expgalaxy=
beneficiaryv1-PUT/beneficiaries/id" class=3D"toc-link" rel=3D"nofollow">PUT=
 /beneficiaries/id</a></span></li>
<li><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"5"><a class=3D"toc-link" =
href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/exp-galaxy-benef=
iciary-v1#expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-PATCH/beneficiaries/ids" rel=3D"nofollow">=
PATCH /beneficiaries/ids</a></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span class=3D"toc-item-body" data-outline=3D"5">More detail can be foun=
d at the page below:</span></p>
<p>EXP API for beneficiary management -&nbsp;<a href=3D"/display/ARTC/exp-g=
alaxy-beneficiary-v1">exp-galaxy-beneficiary-v1</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Vouch call responses reference:</strong></p>
<p><strong><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/Ping+Auth+-+PDP+Errors">Ping Auth - PDP=
 Errors</a></strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Entitlement Query changes&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>Only use case for May will be to return consumer App a list of beneficia=
ries the customer is entitled to view:&nbsp; (create / update / delete acti=
on should be stopped with a vouch call)</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Example request context Format&nbsp;</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Context Format</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
    "query": [
        {
          "attribute": "RequestAttributes.BeneficiaryId"
        }
    ],
    "context": {
        "action": "QUERY",
        "attributes": {
            "RequestAttributes.CustomerUserId": "07a975e0-0a90-4e1c-96d1-c2=
a1e5dcc5a2",
            "RequestAttributes.OrganisationId": "51091430080",=20
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; "RequestAttributes.RequestAction"=
: "VIEW_BENEFICIARY"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
